A4595 &Cx1f; tad-z
r i BC-GLASS-COLUMN-$ADV17-C     09-14 0592
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GLASS-COLUMN-$ADV17-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COMMENTARY: THE HOLBROOKE FACTOR
 &HT;    Moving in the (k) commentary and (i) international categories
for release Sunday, Sept. 17.
