<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-14 13:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4877 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k BC-BUSH-NORTHWEST-SLATE-     09-14 0908
