<P>
   HOME-BANQUET (Undated) _ Pulling off a meal for 60 people
requires an extraordinary level of planning, plenty of advance
work, the assistance of as many skilled friends as you can find,
and flexibility. By Joe Yonan. 1160 words; includes recipes.
</P>
<P>
   HANDYMAN-HOTTON (Undated) _ Wood is better than rubber for
garden edging. By Peter C. Hotton.
</P>
<P>
