Thursday that they had arrested a former senior national police
official in connection with the government's ongoing investigation
of corruption and smuggling in the southern port city of Xiamen,
the highest level arrest so far in the billowing billion dollar
smuggling scandal. By Elisabeth Rosenthal.
</P>
