during Opening Ceremonies. You'll see no macho Big Orange or Nascar
rumble here. This is a real tear-jerker -- Home Depot likes to show
off its sensitive side during the Olympics. The ad focuses on
athletes at their moment of triumph and defeat. (Bond, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 10. WITH PHOTO.
