<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-14 19:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5594 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-OLY-OPENING-ART-680&AMP;A     09-14 1420
